org.apache.poi.poifs.dev

Interface POIFSViewable

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DirectoryNode, DirectoryProperty, DocumentNode, DocumentProperty, POIFSDocument, POIFSFileSystem, Property, RootProperty, TempFilePOIFSFileSystem 

    public interface POIFSViewable
    Interface for a drill-down viewable object. Such an object has content that may or may not be displayed, at the discretion of the viewer. The content is returned to the viewer as an array or as an Iterator, and the object provides a clue as to which technique the viewer should use to get its content. A POIFSViewable object is also expected to provide a short description of itself, that can be used by a viewer when the viewable object is collapsed.(向下钻取可查看对象的接口。此类对象的内容可以由观看者自行决定，也可以不显示。内容以数组或迭代器的形式返回给查看者，并且对象提供了有关查看者应该使用哪种技术来获取其内容的线索。POIFSViewable对象还应提供对其自身的简短描述，以便在折叠可查看对象时供查看者使用。)
    Author:
    Marc Johnson (mjohnson at apache dot org)
